WEBVTT

00:13:59.341 --> 00:14:01.776
Sigurno ste to doživjeli. Ja jesam.

00:14:01.800 --> 00:14:04.435
Probudite se i dok uranjate u svjesnost,

00:14:04.459 --> 00:14:07.650
osjećate taj strašan strah,

00:14:07.674 --> 00:14:09.675
znate, taj istinski jad,

00:14:09.699 --> 00:14:12.381
i odmah, misli se otmu kontroli.

00:14:12.405 --> 00:14:15.485
Počnete misliti na gluposti
koje vas čekaju na poslu

00:14:15.509 --> 00:14:17.217
i na to brdo mailova

00:14:17.241 --> 00:14:20.136
kojih se nikada nećete riješiti,

00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:21.986
pozive koje morate uzvratiti,

00:14:22.010 --> 00:14:23.882
na važan sastanak
na drugom kraju grada,

00:14:23.906 --> 00:14:25.945
morat ćete se probijati u prometu,

00:14:25.969 --> 00:14:27.690
zakasnit ćete po djecu,

00:14:27.714 --> 00:14:29.852
pas vam je bolestan,
a što skuhati za večeru?

00:14:29.852 --> 00:14:31.745
O, moj Bože.